g_{\mu\nu}(\Xi) = \mathbb{E}\left[ \frac{\partial \log p(\text{data} \mid \Xi)}{\partial \Xi^\mu} \frac{\partial \log p(\text{data} \mid \Xi)}{\partial \Xi^\nu} \right]

