Theorem 8 (Optimal Recursive Path). The optimal recursive trajectory minimizing entropy production is a geodesic on (\mathcal{M}, g).

Proof. The path minimizing the thermodynamic action \int L(\Xi, \dot{\Xi}) dt satisfies the geodesic equation:

\ddot{\Xi}^\mu + \Gamma^\mu_{\alpha\beta} \dot{\Xi}^\alpha \dot{\Xi}^\beta = 0

